dct_description_sm: Prepared and published by National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours, hachures, and spot heights. "From Peruvian charts to 2004." "Copyright restrictions of the country of origin continue to exist." "Soundings in meters." Includes compilation diagram. Georeferenced nautical chart. Map no. 22125.
This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
